Hello, thank you for contacting West Barnstable Horse Hides, the family-friendly bowling alley! My name is Jamie, and I'll be assisting you with billing today. May I have your name, please?

Hi Jamie, my name is Alex.

Nice to meet you, Alex! How can I assist you with your billing query?

I received my latest bill, and I think there might be a mistake in the charges.

I'm sorry to hear that. Could you please provide me with your billing account number? It's the one that usually starts with two four seven.

Sure, my billing account number is two four seven six five three one.

Thank you, Alex. I'll look into that for you. Just to verify, could you also provide me with the last four digits of the credit card we have on file?

The last four digits are eight nine zero two.

Great, thank you. I'll take a moment to review your account. I have located the discrepancy and it looks like there was a duplicate charge. We will be removing the incorrect charge and you should see the adjustment on your next billing cycle.

Thank you, Jamie. That clears up my concern.

You're welcome, Alex! Thank you for calling West Barnstable Horse Hides. If you have any more questions, feel free to reach out. Have a great day!
